## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of privacy legislation across different jurisdictions. Additionally, the interpretation of privacy laws can vary, and legal advice should be sought for specific cases. The report is based on data available up to October 2023, and legislative changes after this date are not reflected.

